The ''Slovenia national under-21 football team'' is the national under-21 football team of [[Slovenia]] and is controlled by the [[Football Association of Slovenia]].

==Current squad==
The following players were named for [[2013 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship qualification Group 2|qualifying EURO 2013]] match against [[Lithuania national under-21 football team|Lithuania]] on November 10, 2011.

